-- NCAA Target of Proposed Class Action Suit on Athletic Scholarship Limits
-- B y   V i v e k   S h a n k a r
-- 2010-10-25T18:39:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-25/ncaa-target-of-proposed-class-action-suit-on-athletic-scholarship-limits.html
 The National Collegiate Athletic
Association was named the defendant in a proposed national
class-action lawsuit claiming it violated federal law by
conspiring with colleges and universities to impose artificial
limits on sports scholarships.  The case was filed in the U.S. District Court for the
Northern District of California, a law firm said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vivek Shankar at 
 vshankar3@bloomberg.net  